00:22:14,950 --> 00:22:17,200
你也知道为了达到目标 他都做了些什么
And you know what he's already done to get it.

334
00:22:19,370 --> 00:22:20,500
你知道什么 
So what do you know?

335
00:22:20,580 --> 00:22:22,910
我知道他不喜欢引人注目 这是肯定的
I know he doesn't like this attention, that's for sure.

336
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:30,450
我知道玛雅想追捕浪人的执念 是很危险的
I know Maya's obsession, wanting to hunt Ronin down, is dangerous.

337
00:22:31,450 --> 00:22:33,370
那会干扰她的判断 你说呢 
Clouds her judgment, don't you think?

338
00:22:33,830 --> 00:22:38,620
所以你在担心这个组织 还有…我的位置 
So you're concerned for the organization? And, uh... And my rank in it?

339
00:22:40,580 --> 00:22:41,580
你想要什么 
What do you want?

340
00:22:42,620 --> 00:22:44,080
我不想闹出任何人命
I don't want anybody else to die.

341
00:22:46,790 --> 00:22:49,410
但是玛雅的复仇心态会让她送命
But Maya's need for vengeance is gonna get her killed.

342
00:22:50,870 --> 00:22:51,910
就是这样
Period.

343
00:22:55,580 --> 00:22:59,580
你在找这个吗  还是座位下面的匕首 
Looking for this? Or maybe it's the box cutter under the seat.

344
00:22:59,660 --> 00:23:00,830
你说完了吗 
Look, are we done here?

345
00:23:02,290 --> 00:23:03,700
她在追捕的是一个幽灵
She's chasing a ghost.

346
00:23:05,790 --> 00:23:09,330
我觉得你明白 但是我没法说服她
I think you know that. But I can't convince her of that.

347
00:23:10,290 --> 00:23:12,700
我认为你是唯一能说服她的人
And I'm guessing you're the only one who can.

348
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:18,200
这是最后的警告 你看着办
This is the final warning. Just get it done.

349
00:23:19,950 --> 00:23:21,870
能把枪还给我吗 
Hey, can I have my gun back?

350
00:23:21,950 --> 00:23:23,410
你想什么呢 
Yeah, what do you think?

351
00:23:28,540 --> 00:23:29,750
该死
Ah, come on.

352
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,660
-朋友你来了 -你好
-There's our guy. -Hey.

353
00:23:41,750 --> 00:23:43,700
来点饼干吗 刚烤出来的
Snickerdoodle? They're still warm.

354
00:23:43,790 --> 00:23:45,620
-好的 -进来吧
-Okay. -Hey, come on in.

355
00:23:45,700 --> 00:23:48,500
-克林特 你那边怎么样 -你好
-Hey, Clint. How'd your day go? -Hi.

356
00:23:48,580 --> 00:23:52,500
挺顺利的 你呢 
My, uh... My day's been fine. How are you doing?

357
00:23:52,580 --> 00:23:55,200
很好 我觉得比你那边还顺利
Great, yeah. Better than yours, I'd say.

358
00:23:56,750 --> 00:23:59,620
拿到我的装备了吗 
So did you, uh, get my gear?

359
00:23:59,700 --> 00:24:01,290
拿到了 正在来的路上
Yeah, yeah. They're on the way.

360
00:24:01,370 --> 00:24:03,700
应该很快就到了 别着急
They should be here any minute. Yeah, relax.

361
00:24:04,250 --> 00:24:05,500
-什么  -你看看
-What? -Check that out.

362
00:24:07,580 --> 00:24:09,830
说实话 我穿维京服饰还挺好看的
Not gonna lie, I look pretty good as a Viking.

363
00:24:09,910 --> 00:24:13,410
-你知道吗 这都是我自己做的 -不可能
-I... You know, I made this myself. -No way!

364
00:24:13,500 --> 00:24:16,290
-纯手工的 -你能不能帮我做一件
-By hand. -Could I hire you to make my next one?

365
00:24:16,370 --> 00:24:18,410
当然可以
Oh, yeah. I would love to.

366
00:24:18,500 --> 00:24:21,870
等等 要不咱们谈个条件 
Hey, wait a second. What if that's our deal?

367
00:24:21,950 --> 00:24:25,370
-什么条件  -我们帮你拿到箭头和情报
-What deal? -We get you the arrows and info,

368
00:24:25,450 --> 00:24:27,950
你帮我们找点做新衣服的材料
and you get us materials for a new costume.

369
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:33,700
这样吧 给你们足够的材料做衣服 你们再多做两件行不行 
Okay, how about enough materials to make your costumes plus two more?

370
00:24:35,290 --> 00:24:37,750
我知道有人也需要帮忙做衣服
I know a certain someone who needs a little help with theirs.

371
00:24:39,250 --> 00:24:40,540
-同意 -太棒了
-I'm in. -Great!

372
00:24:40,620 --> 00:24:43,950
奥沃尔 你听见了吗  咱们有新衣服了
Hey, Orval, you hear that? We gettin' new costumes.

373
00:24:44,040 --> 00:24:48,200
凯特 我就是让你把我的箭头拿回来 没让你去舞台指导
Uh, Kate, I asked you to simply retrieve my arrows, not stage a play.

374
00:24:48,290 --> 00:24:49,830
咱们…咱们可是工会啊
Uh, we're a... We're a guild.

375
00:24:51,410 --> 00:24:54,000
劳拉：劳力士并没有 在复仇者联盟基地被摧毁

376
00:24:54,080 --> 00:24:56,910
发射器的信号来自这个地址 格弗里路3715号

377
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:59,040
好的 我该走了
Okay. I gotta go.

378
00:25:00,120 --> 00:25:02,040
咱们该走了 咱们可是一起的 对吗 
We gotta go. We're in this together, right?

379
00:25:02,120 --> 00:25:04,120
-不好意思 抱歉 -你赶紧换衣服
-Excuse me, sorry. -You're gonna have to change.

380
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:05,160
-鹰眼 -你好
-Hawkeye. -Oh, hi.

381
00:25:05,250 --> 00:25:07,290
箭头回收任务完成
Arrow Retrieval Mission complete.

382
00:25:07,370 --> 00:25:09,500
太好了 非常感谢 太谢谢了
Oh, yes. Thank you so much. Appreciate it.

383
00:25:09,580 --> 00:25:10,660
这是我的包
This is my bag.

384
00:25:12,910 --> 00:25:14,830
-是啊 -你自己没带包吗 
-Okay. -You didn't bring your own bag?

385
00:25:15,700 --> 00:25:16,830
没有 我的意思是…
No, I mean...

386
00:25:16,910 --> 00:25:20,750
这个包是我的爱人给我的 上面有刺绣 写着〝热辣女郎〟
My wife gave me this bag. It's embroidered. It says "Bombshell."

387
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:23,370
我看见了 这对你很重要
I... I can see that, that it's very important to you.

388
00:25:23,450 --> 00:25:25,450
他会还给你的 我帮你盯着
He'll get it back to you. Yeah, I'll make sure of it.

389
00:25:26,620 --> 00:25:27,830
-行吗  -我保证
-Right? -I promise.

390
00:25:27,910 --> 00:25:28,950
-走吧 -好吧
-Let's go. -Right. Okay.

391
00:25:29,040 --> 00:25:30,290
-谢谢你 回头见 -好的
-Thank you. See ya. -Okay then.

392
00:25:30,370 --> 00:25:31,950
-非常感谢 -这包真漂亮
-Thank you so much. -Beautiful bag.

393
00:25:32,040 --> 00:25:33,120
谢谢
Thank you.

394
00:25:42,370 --> 00:25:44,450
咱们来这干什么 
You wanna tell me what we're doing here?

395
00:25:44,540 --> 00:25:47,540
我有个重要的东西 正在从那个公寓里发出信号
Something very important to me is pinging inside that apartment.

396
00:25:47,620 --> 00:25:50,580
它是从黑市拍卖上被偷走的 我得拿回来
It was stolen from a black market auction. I need it back.

397
00:25:51,120 --> 00:25:53,750
没有亮灯 也没有人
No lights, no movement.

398
00:25:55,790 --> 00:25:56,910
机不可失
This is our chance.

399
00:25:57,500 --> 00:26:00,000
在更高的屋顶上可能更容易进去
This would have been easier if we were on a higher rooftop.

400
00:26:00,080 --> 00:26:01,120
那是你的想法
That's what you think.

401
00:26:02,120 --> 00:26:04,370
对 没错 要不我这么说呢
Yeah, exactly. That's why I said it.

402
00:26:04,450 --> 00:26:08,120
凯特 永远要首先想怎么快速脱身 然后才是怎么快速进场
Kate, you always wanna prioritize a quick exit over a quick entrance

403
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:10,910
如果事情出了偏差 这是常事
so when things go sideways, and they usually do,

404
00:26:11,620 --> 00:26:14,660
你就做好了脱身的准备 所以我才选择了这个位置
you have an exit strategy. That's why I chose this spot.

405
00:26:14,750 --> 00:26:17,160
我在这里能看到所有的出口
It's got good sightlines for all my exits.

406
00:26:17,700 --> 00:26:19,830
进去很容易 大概花个
Entry should be easy.

407
00:26:19,910 --> 00:26:22,000
三分半钟就能进去
Think it should take me about three and a half minutes to get in.

408
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:25,750
如果你看见什么异常情况 给我个信号 凯特 好吗 
So, if you see anything out here, just give me a signal, Kate. All right?

409
00:26:28,500 --> 00:26:29,410
凯特 
Kate?

410
00:26:32,410 --> 00:26:33,580
你干什么呢 
What're you doin?

411
00:26:36,120 --> 00:26:37,750
凯特 
Kate? Kate?

412
00:26:37,830 --> 00:26:40,500
-不客气 -我说了你是负责盯梢的
-There you are. -I told you you're supposed to be lookout.

413
00:26:40,580 --> 00:26:43,950
对 但是咱们两个里 你觉得 谁在那上面注意力更集中 
Yeah, but of the two of us, who do you trust up there not to get distracted?

414
00:26:44,040 --> 00:26:45,750
这不公平 你仗着自己是个孩子
That's not fair, that your inability

415
00:26:45,830 --> 00:26:48,910
就这样随心所欲胡搅蛮缠
to act like a grown-up helps you get your way.

416
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:52,330
是不公平 但是这不就是人生嘛
No, it's not. But it is what it is.

417
00:26:53,450 --> 00:26:56,370
你得用钩索箭把自己荡进去
I need you to use your grappling hook arrow to anchor yourself in.

418
00:26:56,450 --> 00:26:58,620
从建筑的一侧移动到窗户那里
Propel down the side of the building to the window.

419
00:26:58,700 --> 00:27:01,410
如果锁住了 就轻轻地把它打碎
If it's locked, break in quietly.

420
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:04,870
好的 计划不错 天衣无缝 但是需要一点点调整
Yeah, love all of that. Great plan, just a slight tweak though.

421
00:27:04,950 --> 00:27:07,620
晚上好 先生 我来帮你拿包吧
Good evening, sir. Can I help you with your bags?

422
00:27:08,290 --> 00:27:09,290
-谢谢你 -没事
- Oh. Thank you. - Sure.

423
00:27:09,370 --> 00:27:10,910
你在干什么…不
What are you... No, no, no.

424
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:13,160
不行 别惊动别人
No, no, no. Don't... Don't engage.

425
00:27:13,250 --> 00:27:15,580
-你买了芹菜 还有麦片 -凯特
- Got celery, a little Kashi. - Kate.

426
00:27:15,660 --> 00:27:16,870
还有椒盐面包 
Okay, some pretzels?

427
00:27:18,080 --> 00:27:19,000
你在哪 
Where are you?

428
00:27:19,080 --> 00:27:21,370
别紧张 我在电梯里
Oh, relax. I'm taking the elevator.

429
00:27:21,450 --> 00:27:22,700
不好意思 你说什么 
I'm sorry, what was that?

430
00:27:24,660 --> 00:27:27,580
抱歉 我没和您说话
Oh, I, uh... I'm sorry, I wasn't talking to you.

431
00:27:30,870 --> 00:27:32,540
我告诉你个秘密吧 
Can I tell you a secret?

432
00:27:32,620 --> 00:27:33,870
别这么做
Please don't do this.

433
00:27:33,950 --> 00:27:35,750
我在和一个复仇者通话
I was talking to an Avenger.

434
00:27:36,870 --> 00:27:38,160
我们用耳机联络
He's in my ear.

435
00:27:38,250 --> 00:27:39,750
你应该闭嘴了
Maybe you should stop talking.

436
00:27:39,830 --> 00:27:41,330
对 我是他的搭档
Yeah, I'm his partner.

437
00:27:41,410 --> 00:27:42,910
把这个还给我吧
I'll just take this back.

438
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:45,160
我能帮您拿到门口的 没关系
I can help you to the door, no problem.

439
00:27:45,250 --> 00:27:47,700
不用了 给我就行了
No, that's all right. I got it from here.

440
00:27:47,790 --> 00:27:50,120
好吧 你确定吗 真的没关系的
Okay, are you sure? It's really no problem.

441
00:27:51,370 --> 00:27:52,830
好吧 您多小心
All right, you take care now.

442
00:27:54,120 --> 00:27:56,500
弓这么大你平时怎么处理啊
What do you do with this giant bow problem?

443
00:27:57,080 --> 00:27:58,410
我有个可折叠的
I have a collapsible one.

444
00:27:59,330 --> 00:28:00,870
原来如此
Oh, that makes sense.

445
00:28:02,370 --> 00:28:05,250
好吧 我到门口了
Okay. I'm at the door.

446
00:28:06,250 --> 00:28:07,370
没有异常
We're good.

447
00:28:32,120 --> 00:28:35,500
好的 客厅没问题
Okay. Living room's all clear.

448
00:28:37,330 --> 00:28:38,410
该死
Oh, shit.

449
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:43,790
怎么了 
What was that?

450
00:28:44,750 --> 00:28:47,660
我不知道 墙上好像有频闪灯
I don't know. There are, like, strobe lights attached to the wall.

451
00:28:47,750 --> 00:28:50,580
-什么频闪灯  -我不知道
- What do you mean, strobe lights? - I don't know.

452
00:28:51,370 --> 00:28:52,660
你看见什么了 
Yeah, what do you see?

453
00:28:53,330 --> 00:28:55,250
好吧 我要找什么 
Okay, what am I lookin' for?

454
00:28:55,950 --> 00:28:58,620
一块表 古董劳力士
A watch, vintage Rolex.

455
00:28:59,620 --> 00:29:01,370
是我以前的同事的
Belongs to someone I used to work with.

456
00:29:01,910 --> 00:29:03,450
就这点信息吗 克林特 
Is that the whole story, Clint?

457
00:29:03,540 --> 00:29:05,410
他们已经退出很多年了
They've been out of the game a long time,

458
00:29:05,500 --> 00:29:07,830
但是他们的身份都储存在那块表里
but their identity is still attached to that watch.

459
00:29:07,910 --> 00:29:10,250
如果被运动服黑帮发现了呢 
Hmm. And if the Tracksuits find out about it?

460
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:14,160
他们的身份就会曝光 那些朋友就永别了
It would blow their cover. Goodbye, friend.

461
00:29:22,250 --> 00:29:23,370
拿到手表了
Got the watch.

462
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:26,160
太好了
Great.

463
00:29:29,910 --> 00:29:30,910
等等
Hang on a minute.

464
00:29:33,370 --> 00:29:35,750
克林特 有人在记录你的家人
Clint, somebody is taking notes on your family.

465
00:29:35,830 --> 00:29:36,870
什么 
What?

466
00:29:36,950 --> 00:29:39,410
〝克林特·巴顿 妻子劳拉 女儿莱拉 14岁〟
"Clint Barton, wife, Laura, daughter, Lila, age 14,

467
00:29:39,500 --> 00:29:42,330
〝儿子 库珀 16岁 内特〟 这是…
"son, Cooper, age 16, son, Nate." What...

468
00:29:42,410 --> 00:29:44,290
凯特 赶紧出来
Kate, get out of there now.

469
00:29:44,370 --> 00:29:46,080
什么 为什么 
What? Why?

470
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:49,540
那个灯是个警报 是给聋哑人用的无声警报
That light's an alarm. It's a silent alarm for people that can't hear.

471
00:29:49,620 --> 00:29:50,790
天啊
Oh, my God.

472
00:29:50,870 --> 00:29:51,950
这是玛雅的公寓
It's Maya's apartment.

473
00:29:52,040 --> 00:29:53,750
好吧 我来了…
All right, I'm coming...

474
00:29:55,040 --> 00:29:56,620
克林特 怎么了 
Clint, what's going on?

475
00:29:58,410 --> 00:29:59,330
克林特 
Clint?

476
00:30:04,870 --> 00:30:05,790
玛雅在这
Maya's here.

477
00:30:05,870 --> 00:30:07,200
对 我看见了
Yeah, I can see that.

478
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:09,410
你为什么不告诉我 
Then why didn't you tell me?

479
00:30:10,160 --> 00:30:12,450
我告诉你了 玛雅和我在屋顶上
I did. Maya's on the roof with me.

480
00:30:12,830 --> 00:30:15,290
不对 玛雅分明在这里
No, Maya is definitely here.

481
00:30:18,950 --> 00:30:20,750
那和我打斗的是谁 
Well, who the hell am I fighting then?

482
00:30:24,450 --> 00:30:25,660
需要帮忙吗 
A little help?

483
00:30:27,040 --> 00:30:30,660
等我一下 来了
Give me a second. Incoming.

484
00:30:33,870 --> 00:30:34,950
到钩索上去
Get on the zip line.

485
00:30:53,700 --> 00:30:54,870
这下好了
Oh, this is great.

486
00:30:57,660 --> 00:30:59,120
快啊
Come on. Come on.

487
00:31:08,330 --> 00:31:09,410
疼死了
That hurt.

488
00:31:49,370 --> 00:31:51,910
不要
No, no, no! No, no!

489
00:32:04,580 --> 00:32:05,580
把我拉上去
Pull me up!

490
00:32:09,580 --> 00:32:10,500
赶紧走
Get outta here.

491
00:33:32,330 --> 00:33:33,410
那是什么人 
Who the hell was that?

492
00:33:34,620 --> 00:33:36,000
你没必要知道 凯特
You don't wanna know, Kate.

493
00:33:36,080 --> 00:33:38,830
你不告诉我怎么回事 咱们没法做搭档
I cannot be your partner if you don't tell me what's going on.

494
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:42,330
你不是我的搭档 你明白吗 
You're not my partner. Do you understand that?

495
00:33:42,410 --> 00:33:43,290
你从来都不是
You never were.

496
00:33:45,290 --> 00:33:48,250
有人雇佣了黑寡妇来当刺客
Someone has hired a Black Widow assassin.

497
00:33:49,950 --> 00:33:52,750
情况很严重 很紧急
This has gotten very real, very quickly.

498
00:33:54,040 --> 00:33:55,500
我得自己行动了
So I'm doing this alone.

499
00:33:57,580 --> 00:33:58,700
不行 你不能这么做
No, you're not.

500
00:34:00,870 --> 00:34:04,000
我知道今天晚上确实出了些意外 但是我是自愿来的
Look, I know that tonight didn't go as planned, but I chose to be here.

501
00:34:04,080 --> 00:34:06,910
我知道有风险 我都知道
I understand the risk, I understand all of that.

502
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:08,290
我不能这么做
I'm not gonna do it.

503
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:10,120
你听见了吗 
Do you hear me?

504
00:34:12,620 --> 00:34:13,450
你听见了吗 
Do you hear me?

